Kubo C, Day NK, Good RA.

Reduced food intake doubles and even triples the life span of (NZB X NZW)F1 
(B/W) mice and greatly influences of food intake while keeping vitamin and 
mineral intake constant in mice of the MRL/Mp-lpr/lpr (MRL/l) strain. 
